I sincerely request the Coke Studios Management to look into setting up a healthy, creative and extremely entertaining festival to bring the world together by Coke Studios from so many countries of the world with extremely entertaining creations attracting people of the world regardless of their mother tongue. Pakistan Coke Studio may be the best of them. I was in
Canada in 1969 when Woodstock Music Festival was held in the US. It was a unique and most famous festival of the creative artists. I think it is about time to have a similar and even better and greater COKE STUDIOS MUSIC FESTIVAL.

snippet.textDisplay:
Beautiful ! Awesome ! 

The music , the instruments , the voices , the combination, all together took it to another level.

WOW  "Allaaaaaah"   in the end was epic .
 Indeed Masha-Allah ! 

Truly Divine inspires many different people toward Him in many multiple beautiful ways. Hence there is no one way &  that is the beauty of Divine. 

Moves the soul up high.

Would really request if you would kindly bring in  the epic of another Janoon's  song "Zamanai ke Andaaz  Badle" with another combination of their music. 
The lyrics have a great meaning for every present & future  generations. So hope we could one day look forward to it. 

Congratulations  , Coke Studio   keep going. Love from UK 👍
